@{
    ViewBag.Title = "FAQ";
}

<h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

<div class="panel panel-default">
    <div class="panel-heading"><strong>What services does CozyPaws provide?</strong></div>
    <div class="panel-body">
        CozyPaws provides pet boarding, booking management, and pet care support.
    </div>
</div>

<div class="panel panel-default">
    <div class="panel-heading"><strong>Do I need an account to make a booking?</strong></div>
    <div class="panel-body">
        Yes, pet owners need to register and log in before managing pets or creating bookings.
    </div>
</div>

<div class="panel panel-default">
    <div class="panel-heading"><strong>Can I update my pet information?</strong></div>
    <div class="panel-body">
        Yes, after logging in, you can manage your pets through the pet owner dashboard.
    </div>
</div>